{"id":9299,"date":"2026-03-20T16:48:17","date_gmt":"2026-03-20T09:48:17","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=9299"},"modified":"2026-03-20T16:48:17","modified_gmt":"2026-03-20T09:48:17","slug":"nmn-nicotinamide-mononucleotide","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/nmn-nicotinamide-mononucleotide\/","title":{"rendered":"NMN (Nicotinamide Mononucleotide) ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t \u201ctr\u1ebb h\u00f3a t\u1ebf b\u00e0o\u201d"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"gioi-thieu-chung-ve-nmn-nicotinamide-mononucleotide\"><\/span><b>Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u chung v\u1ec1 NMN (Nicotinamide Mononucleotide)<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_9302\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-9302\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-9302 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NMN-2.webp\" alt=\"\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u00f3a sinh c\u1ee7a NMN trong ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NMN-2.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NMN-2-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NMN-2-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NMN-2-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-9302\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u00f3a sinh c\u1ee7a NMN trong ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da<span style=\"font-size: 16px\">\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">\u00a0<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00ean khoa h\u1ecdc: \u03b2-Nicotinamide Mononucleotide (NMN)<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c ph\u00e2n t\u1eed: C\u2081\u2081H\u2081\u2085N\u2082O\u2088P<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u00f3m: Ti\u1ec1n ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a NAD\u207a (Nicotinamide Adenine Dinucleotide) \u2013 coenzyme c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong m\u1ecdi t\u1ebf b\u00e0o s\u1ed1ng.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c: NMN \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb niacinamide (vitamin B3). C\u00e1c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y cho th\u1ea5y vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 sung NMN (qua \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng u\u1ed1ng ho\u1eb7c b\u00f4i ngo\u00e0i) c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec m\u1ee9c NAD\u207a, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt: David Sinclair (\u0110H Harvard) l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00ean phong nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a NMN trong ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 sinh h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dac-diem-hoat-chat-nmn-nicotinamide-mononucleotide\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t NMN (Nicotinamide Mononucleotide)<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-dung-noi-bat\"><\/span><b>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-9303 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NMN-3.webp\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng NMN trong skincare b\u00f4i thoa\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NMN-3.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NMN-3-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NMN-3-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NMN-3-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">NMN \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u201cngu\u1ed3n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u1ebb h\u00f3a\u201d cho t\u1ebf b\u00e0o v\u00ec c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u0103ng n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 NAD\u207a \u2013 ph\u00e2n t\u1eed c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa DNA, trao \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng oxy ho\u00e1.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u0103ng n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ebf b\u00e0o: th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a ty th\u1ec3 \u2013 \u201cnh\u00e0 m\u00e1y n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u201d trong t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1: h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 enzyme Sirtuin \u2013 nh\u00f3m protein \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd t\u1ebf b\u00e0o, gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i, gi\u1ea3m n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 DNA: gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ee9t g\u00e3y chu\u1ed7i DNA do tia UV v\u00e0 stress oxy ho\u00e1.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da: c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o v\u00e0 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t melanin.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o da: nh\u1edd ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 niacinamide trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam, t\u0103ng t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p ceramide v\u00e0 lipid bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-che-hoat-dong\"><\/span><b>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sau khi h\u1ea5p thu, NMN \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n ho\u00e1 th\u00e0nh NAD\u207a, m\u1ed9t coenzyme then ch\u1ed1t trong h\u00f4 h\u1ea5p t\u1ebf b\u00e0o v\u00e0 s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa DNA. NAD\u207a tham gia h\u01a1n 500 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng sinh h\u1ecdc, bao g\u1ed3m:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u00edch ho\u1ea1t enzyme Sirtuin (SIRT1\u2013SIRT7) \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Duy tr\u00ec n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho t\u1ebf b\u00e0o s\u1eebng v\u00e0 nguy\u00ean b\u00e0o s\u1ee3i, gi\u00fap da ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 enzyme PARP trong vi\u1ec7c s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa DNA b\u1ecb h\u01b0 h\u1ea1i do UV.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u00f3i ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn, NMN gi\u00fap th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o cho t\u1ebf b\u00e0o, l\u00e0m ch\u1eadm qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh suy gi\u1ea3m ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng theo tu\u1ed5i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dang-bao-che-thuong-gap\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea1ng b\u00e0o ch\u1ebf th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Serum ho\u1eb7c ampoule ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1: ch\u1ee9a 0,1\u20131% NMN, th\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p peptide ho\u1eb7c hyaluronic acid.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/kem-duong-sang-mela-gsc\/\">Mua ngay: B\u1ed9 S\u1ea3n Ph\u1ea9m X\u1eed L\u00fd N\u00e1m Ch\u1ee9a NMN<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/tinh-chat-duong-sang-ngay-mela-gsc\/\">Serum ng\u00e0y<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/tinh-chat-duong-sang-dem-mela-gsc\/\">Serum \u0111\u00eam,<\/a>\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/kem-duong-sang-mela-gsc\/\">Kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng<\/a><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng da: k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p niacinamide, adenosine, vitamin E.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ea1ng vi\u00ean u\u1ed1ng (th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m b\u1ed5 sung): 125\u2013500 mg\/ng\u00e0y \u2013 kh\u00f4ng thu\u1ed9c nh\u00f3m m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m. (Tuy nhi\u00ean hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i NMN \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng u\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n v\u01b0\u1edbng nhi\u1ec1u tranh c\u00e3i v\u00e0 nghi\u00eam c\u1ea5m \u1edf th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng, kh\u00f4ng khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch)<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng: d\u00f9ng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m s\u00e2u, th\u00edch h\u1ee3p sau \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-su-dung-nmn-nicotinamide-mononucleotide\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng NMN (Nicotinamide Mononucleotide)<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"doi-tuong-su-dung\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da m\u1ea5t s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng, x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u, thi\u1ebfu n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n, ch\u00f9ng nh\u00e3o.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da ch\u1ecbu stress oxy ho\u00e1 do n\u1eafng, \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m, th\u1ee9c khuya.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da sau 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u suy gi\u1ea3m t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 da treatment, do \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh ch\u1ed1ng vi\u00eam nh\u1eb9.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-dung-%e2%80%93-lieu-luong\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng \u2013 li\u1ec1u l\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9ng 1\u20132 l\u1ea7n m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, th\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf b\u01b0\u1edbc serum ho\u1eb7c kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi d\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a NMN, n\u00ean tr\u00e1nh \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng m\u1ea1nh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ngay sau b\u00f4i. n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng, v\u00ec NAD\u207a c\u00f3 t\u00ednh nh\u1ea1y s\u00e1ng nh\u1eb9.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n da th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 sau 4\u20138 tu\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-hop-nmn-sao-cho-hieu-qua\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p NMN sao cho hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">NMN + Niacinamide: t\u0103ng s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t NAD\u207a n\u1ed9i sinh, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ebf b\u00e0o nhanh h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">NMN + Peptide: c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9 s\u0103n ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">NMN + Vitamin C: t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed1ng oxy ho\u00e1 v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">NMN + Hyaluronic Acid: gi\u1eef \u1ea9m, gi\u1ea3m kh\u00f4, gi\u00fap da t\u01b0\u01a1i kh\u1ecfe.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-chong-chi-dinh-nmn-nicotinamide-mononucleotide\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd &amp; Ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh NMN (Nicotinamide Mononucleotide)<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-9300 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NMN-4.webp\" alt=\"L\u01b0u \u00fd v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh NMN\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NMN-4.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NMN-4-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NMN-4-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NMN-4-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">NMN c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 an to\u00e0n cao, dung n\u1ea1p t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft lo\u1ea1i da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi v\u1edbi acid m\u1ea1nh (AHA, BHA, PHA n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 cao) trong c\u00f9ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m ho\u1ea1t t\u00ednh sinh h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a NMN.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a NMN n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n k\u1ef9, v\u00ec ph\u00e2n t\u1eed d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb oxy ho\u00e1 n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed v\u00e0 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u00e1nh d\u00f9ng n\u1ebfu da \u0111ang b\u1ecb vi\u00eam c\u1ea5p ho\u1eb7c tr\u1ea7y x\u01b0\u1edbc s\u00e2u.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-9304 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NMN-5.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NMN-5.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NMN-5-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NMN-5-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NMN-5-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c NMN kh\u00f4ng?<\/b><b><br \/>\n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 d\u1eef li\u1ec7u d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1ec1 NMN d\u00f9ng ngo\u00e0i da trong thai k\u1ef3, nh\u01b0ng v\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n ch\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a NAD\u207a, nguy c\u01a1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 th\u1ea5p. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u00ean tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u00f9ng c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 cao ho\u1eb7c d\u1ea1ng vi\u00ean u\u1ed1ng trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-bao-quan-nmn-nicotinamide-mononucleotide\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n NMN (Nicotinamide Mononucleotide)<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">NMN nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, nhi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 oxy, n\u00ean c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3i k\u00edn, chai t\u1ed1i m\u00e0u ho\u1eb7c airless.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n \u1edf nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 m\u00e1t (&lt;25\u00b0C), tr\u00e1nh \u00e1nh n\u1eafng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu serum \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00e0u sang v\u00e0ng n\u00e2u ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 m\u00f9i oxy ho\u00e1, n\u00ean ng\u1eebng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>Ngu\u1ed3n tham kh\u1ea3o:<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Brito, S., Baek, J. M., Cha, B., Heo, H., Lee, S. H., Kim, S., &amp; Lim, J. (2022). Nicotinamide mononucleotide reduces melanin production in aged melanocytes by inhibiting cAMP\/Wnt signaling. Journal of Dermatological Science, 106(3), 159\u2013169. <a href=\"https:\/\/doi.org\/10.1016\/j.jds.2022.05.002\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/doi.org\/10.1016\/j.jds.2022.05.002<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Camacho-Pereira, J., Tarrag\u00f3, M. G., Chini, C. C. S., Nin, V., Escande, C., Warner, G. M., Puranik, A. S., Schoon, R. A., Reid, J. M., Galina, A., &amp; Chini, E. N. (2016). CD38 dictates age-related NAD decline and mitochondrial dysfunction through an SIRT3-dependent mechanism. Cell Metabolism, 23(6), 1127\u20131139. <a href=\"https:\/\/doi.org\/10.1016\/j.cmet.2016.05.006\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/doi.org\/10.1016\/j.cmet.2016.05.006<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>NMN (Nicotinamide Mononucleotide) ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u201cnh\u00e0 m\u00e1y n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u201d \u1edf t\u1ea7ng s\u00e2u c\u1ee7a t\u1ebf b\u00e0o. L\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n ch\u1ea5t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a NAD\u207a \u2013 coenzyme thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu trong m\u1ecdi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ed1ng, NMN gi\u00fap ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ch\u1ed1ng oxy ho\u00e1 v\u00e0 l\u00e0m ch\u1eadm d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 t\u1eeb g\u1ed1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":9301,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-9299","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-su-kien"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/9299","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/12"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=9299"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/9299\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":9307,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/9299\/revisions\/9307"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/9301"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=9299"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=9299"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=9299"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}